# ─── Large model artifacts (exceed GitHub 100 MB limit) ──────────────────────
# Segment ensemble pickles (41 MB – 76 MB each)
model_artifacts/ensemble_*.pkl
# Global CatBoost model (76 MB)
model_artifacts/vehicle_price_catboost.cbm
# Global XGBoost model (18 MB)
model_artifacts/vehicle_price_xgboost.json
# Global LightGBM model (kept — only 0.5 MB; remove if you need to slim the repo)
# model_artifacts/vehicle_price_lightgbm.txt

# Small metadata & sample CSVs are NOT ignored (useful for documentation):
# model_artifacts/model_metadata.json  ← ~11 MB — kept
# model_artifacts/training_report.json ← ~11 MB — kept
# model_artifacts/cleaned_training_sample.csv ← ~0.5 MB — kept

